title: Leigh Occhi // 62
description:
In 1992, a 13-year-old girl went missing during a hurricane in Tupelo, Mississippi. When her mother returned home from work, she found a worrisome and questionable scene at the house. and immediately called police. FBI were introduced into the case and the town searched tirelessly for the girl. So what happened to her? This is the disappearance of Leigh Occhi.
